ji\" />"},{"pid":"097be7884801225114c00f6c1ade5ffa46491315","tid":317412,"uid":127323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T23:41:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下poly lower quarter啲數據係點得黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大多數院校下四分位係中位/平均既95-97%"},{"pid":"f8cbb1bf7b41c28824a0673f8fcc9fd37a827dff","tid":317412,"uid":127323,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T23:44:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今年又靠excel食咗幾多條女呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當年位女仔最後咪和好如初<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲一齊影相訴苦傾計<br />\n識佢既巴絲打可證明<br />\n放榜還放榜 excel係用心設計<br />\n真係希望幫到人"},{"pid":"cb43276d8caf6b09d28b110de25d6dcefd10e233","tid":317412,"uid":127323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T23:44:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下 巴打可以點改 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/12/012620_b656dc25f63dde6221edb58d4364f1de.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F12%2F012620_b656dc25f63dde6221edb58d4364f1de.png&h=87b3192a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/12/012620_eb4744b00195aea32f46475f6ce795c1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F12%2F012620_eb4744b00195aea32f46475f6ce795c1.png&h=2541a87c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我會研究下"},{"pid":"61b088805259eb0421c27a5e00709a86545c48bc","tid":317412,"uid":127323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T23:44:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上年用你個excel入左A1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係你既實力"},{"pid":"4b992feba596547a32702af39bd920a8e22905c6","tid":317412,"uid":52101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T23:45:21.000Z","msg":"5*3243<br />\n重考數學通識文學<br />\n升左一分<br />\nBest 5 21<br />\n4c+1x still 19<br />\n想揀中文，求指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f55822bf78e86b70d962e72e989448ff5e167757","tid":317412,"uid":16953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T23:53:40.000Z","msg":"巴打<br />\n433333 bio chem<br />\n可以點排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想入ou nursing <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}